frontmatter.title: New SF Symbols in iOS 14
frontmatter.staticPreview: SF Symbols, the standardized icon system for the Apple ecosystem, got some great upgrades this year. In addition to macOS support, there are almost a thousand more symbols available, and there are some changes in the symbol names...
frontmatter.mdxPreview: [SF Symbols](https://developer.apple.com/design/human-interface-guidelines/sf-symbols/overview/), the standardized icon system for the Apple ecosystem, got some great upgrades this year. In addition to macOS support, there are almost a thousand _more_ symbols available, and there are some changes in the symbol names...
